OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMormon Church fined over   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fclaim it hid investments   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Mormon Church, officially known as 
OL,6, the Church of Jesus Christ of          
OL,7, Latter-day Saints (LDS), and its       
OL,8, investment firm will pay out $5m       
OL,9, (#4.1m) over claims they hid a huge    
OL,10, cache of shares.                       
OL,12,FThe LDS and its investment firm, Ensign
OL,13,FPeak Advisers, used "shell" companies  
OL,14,Fto hide a $32bn stock portfolio, the US
OL,15,FSecurities and Exchange Commission     
OL,16,F(SEC) said.                            
OL,18,FEnsign Peak will pay a $4m penalty and 
OL,19,Fthe Church will pay $1m.               
OL,21,FNeither has admitted any wrongdoing.   
